          "token": "23",
          "kind": "numeric",
          "text": "(a) Radioactive waste includes all material which is discarded, unwanted or has no present lawful economic use, and contains mined or refined naturally occurring isotopes, accelerator produced isotopes and by-product material, source material or special nuclear material as those terms are defined in ORS 453.605.",
